metadata.name: AzuGoal Football Fantasy MysteryBox
metadata.description: This is the MYESTERY BOX of AzuGoal Football Fantasy, which can be opened with basic NFT and grant you access to the Universe of Azugoal. When it is turned on, you will own a Azugoal NFT with basic traits belonging to a specific team in the 2022 Qatar World Cup. AzuGoal NFT brings you different gameplay scenarios where you can win eth token bonuses, play multiple games, find your teammates and lift World Cup with your favorite team in the AzuGoal gameplay universe.
